{"type": "article", "id": 54851, "title": "部分美妆进入中国将无须动物测试，以及，任天堂推出旅行周边 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-07-03T06:35:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 51495, "name": "秋冬高定周"}, {"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}, {"id": 51534, "name": "Zegna"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 916, "name": "任天堂"}, {"id": 45529, "name": "Vetements"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180703143212IZtMbfKcUvDlzdJH.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Uniqlo-inks-deal-with-Roger-Federer-starts-at-Wimbledon,993768.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">费德勒出任优衣库品牌全球大使，10 年合约总计 3 亿美元</a>&nbsp;</strong>|&nbsp;费德勒自 1994 年起与耐克已合作 24 年，最近一份合约于 2018 年 3 月 1 日失效。与优衣库签约意味着从本月的温网开始，费德勒在全年的网球锦标赛中都将身着“Uniqlo”Logo 出场。优衣库创始人柳井正在评价这次合作时说：“这代表我们无论在场上或场下都将有所创新。”不过，费德勒姓名缩写“RF”的商标权仍由耐克集团所有。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://qz.com/1315541/italys-ermenegildo-zegna-invests-in-indian-brand-raghavendra-rathore-jodhpur/\" rel=\"nofollow\">意大利奢侈品牌 Ermenegildo Zegna 注资印度设计师品牌 Raghavendra Rathore Jodhpur</a>&nbsp;</strong>| Zegna 通过与印度零售商 Reliance Brands 合作已在印度市场运营长达 10 年。此次收购的设计师品牌创立已有 24 年，擅长将印度男性常穿的民族服饰班德嘎拉（Bandhgala）现代化。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/-sJK6SMs0R93CZ99OK8HFQ\" rel=\"nofollow\">国际零残忍组织 CFI&nbsp;与中国政府部门达成合作，部分进口美妆品牌进入中国将无须动物测试</a>&nbsp;</strong>|&nbsp;2014 年 6 月起，中国国家食品药品监督管理总局（CFDA）已不再强制要求国产“非特殊用途”日化和化妆品进行动物测试，允许依据现有的原材料安全测试数据，或以欧盟许可的非动物测试来代替。但对进口化妆品并未开放许可。国际零残忍组织 Cruelty Free International 称，他们将与咨询公司 Knudsen CRC 合作，帮助部分国际美妆品牌进入中国市场。<br></p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/kerings-richard-ginori-joins-secoo-online-china-exclusive-1202743675/\" rel=\"nofollow\">开云集团旗下意大利瓷器品牌 Richard Ginori 入驻国内奢侈品电商寺库</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 除在线上推出外，该品牌瓷器也将在寺库的 9 个线下体验中心出售。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><strong>为庆祝 LGBTQ 骄傲月，adidas Originals 找来 10 位名人重新设计了他们各自版本的&nbsp;Samba 球鞋</strong>。</p><p>10 位参与者包括：Marc Jacobs、Pharrell Williams、Kate Moss、Blondey McCoy、Naomi Campbell、Chapman Brothers、Amanda Lepore、Bella Freud、Goldie、Phillip Treacy。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703130946mYMnskUH8zcjyiLG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Chapman Brothers</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703130916mcN4nABdbPgpRraG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Pharrell Williams</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703130925uYjOzJFLbmIAW3VR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Kate Moss</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703130857qRtCWQoSPLGwkIN6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Marc Jacobs</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703130937k6couWFXQfdpO9KJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Amanda Lepore</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807031309550sfE1yMCX4w5x8z7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Blondey McCoy</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703131005x4NeMvGlXdLt7pJz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Goldie</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703131016yNOC3UxqpjrB9n52.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Phillip Treacy</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703131029dMJyCRWneLcaKrHA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Naomi Campbell</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703131039IFkMx29jLmGdrtaA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Bella Freud</figcaption> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/336887/16-kuanchaofengfujijierentiantanglvxingyongpinxiliekaicui/\" rel=\"nofollow\">任天堂推出 16 款旅行用品周边</a></strong>，包括折叠手提袋、存储袋组合、行李箱、拖鞋、颈枕、行李牌、眼罩等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703131310DPSUesf5JrVAxqWR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.100000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703131424kRnjwdNa1r5xOtUf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.100413\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703131456laznMprUZRfP1oCm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807031315479X82DgvLx5MiGKmR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.952500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703131537Ql27V4LnAeWJdBo1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.699167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703131554otQsLly8a4Th2JG5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.630833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703131446ZT6nNVb0zpoWmGE8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.602500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703131507NIWVRCMFmYK2zk8P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807031315194LQBJWi5jxMfbtER.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.474167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703131527vqu65JTpznh0WPRD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.474167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>ColourPop 发售新款眼影盘 “Make Up Your Mind</strong>”，6 个色号均由其 Instagram 账号粉丝投票选出。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703131617TCR2uQLG9HrJvsaV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.vans.com/article_detail/vans-surf-t-and-c-2018.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vans 与有 47 年历史的夏威夷滑板冲浪品牌&nbsp;T&amp;C Surf 合作发布了一个限量胶囊系列</a></strong>。<br></p><p>这个系列包括三款球鞋、两款上衣及一款短裤，印花中融合了 Vans 的经典格纹与 T&amp;C Surf 标志性的阴阳 Logo。三款球鞋分别为&nbsp;Sk8-Hi 138 Decon SF、Authentic SF&nbsp;和 Slide-On。不过，该系列只于 7 月在部分北美门店发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703125321a0Cokjs8FqASdvVO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.563000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807031254045rysmAx4pXW3Id0w.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807031253501miJ0GZd6qwLAH8c.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703125340lO8i4ZvfF92hNqDz.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.021667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Furla-signs-up-international-influencers-for-new-campaign,993853.html#.Wzr-utgzbUo\" rel=\"nofollow\">Furla 2018 秋冬大片找来 6 个 Instagram 网红拍摄</a></strong>。</p><p>6 位网红包括 Sonya Esman、Stefanie Giesinger、Rocky Barnes、Keisuke Asano 和 Vanessa Hong。他们在 Instagram 上的粉丝数合计达到 910 万人。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703125306D0sVjeTgBLGwCX6m.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.644156\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>Vetements 2019 春夏成衣系列在巴黎发布</strong>。</p><p>说不会再参加时装周主日程的 Vetements 又回到了时装周的舞台上。本季&nbsp;Demna Gvasalia 说他想讲个关于家乡格鲁吉亚的故事——“家庭与战争”，格鲁吉亚内战后那些“他儿时未能处理的伤痛”，为此他从格鲁吉亚找来 40 位素人走秀。</p><p>不过从设计本身上看，不算有新意。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703135146znotL7mPM8e5Rfrc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703135200gd1BjKRwkYMrLeo4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703135209mjVqWnhwyMbDXe8r.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703135218oXClsZSWdtaqThpM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703135225f8jObJVSEMULW4wN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703135231NZQ1KriyfVoIM45k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703135243lPAe2KJBwIY7Vmsf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703135253O5NI9H6fZAa0Uu32.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703135303n9puTvW67UzDIM4k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807031353180UTgXdc1eFQnIuwb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703135333PrtwxBLgNWfbeIY6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703135343fdU56cPQS4gtBx8n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703135356CeqEx6QbJtrainBU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703135402vkqewA8n9Ta5t0dQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703135415FgEdz5GslS4DeTiU.jp