> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703135722m1rFWUw45dIjstE9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703135744WypKj8fGXNvTbqE1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703135749MGP0a6jwHDXsNWAq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>2018 秋冬高定周继续：</strong></p><p><strong>Christian Dior 2018 秋冬高定系列</strong>。</p><p>创意总监 Maria Grazia Chiuri 延续了她稳妥保守的作风。设计遵循经典五六十年代礼服裙廓形；材质上，有色彩浓郁的绸缎，接近肤色、薄如蝉纱的纱质面料。一些西装做了女性化处理：收腰、百褶袖。每套 Look 看上去都优雅实穿，但没有一套令人难忘。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703120327mc5QgGNuFOjB7v4T.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703120238F5l0H82hCrcZwDAE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703120251uRNnTrXtAlf3FM0d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703120316fEtZNBY2I08q5hr9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703120338JgkQA9xlSTdijF5V.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703120355UT0JRjl3uXqcvnEp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807031204074q6DEJN2LlCijdVu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807031204227dGuaWT2YJSocpLF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703120434zR8sOZwN6o3MDEgl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </fi